arStrings.szText: Hitting an enemy with a {c_important}Basic{/c} Skill grants you {c_number}[SF_12|1]%{/c} Attack Speed for {c_number}[SF_1|0]{/c} seconds, stacking up to {c_number}[SF_0|0]{/c} times. Upon reaching maximum stacks, you enter a Vampiric Bloodrage, gaining {c_random}[SF_13|1]%{/c}{c_gray}[x]{/c} {c_important}Basic{/c} Skill damage and {c_number}[SF_15|1]%{/c} Movement Speed for {c_number}[SF_11|0]{/c} seconds.
